  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a pan over medium heat and add grated ginger. Cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add sultanas, bhuna, honey, rose water, cinnamon, and cardamom to the pan. Cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add water to the pan and bring to a simmer. Cook for 8 minutes.",
    "Brush the lotus-leaf wraps with a little water and warm them on a baking sheet in the oven at 200°C for 5 minutes.",
    "Spoon the sultana mixture onto a warmed lotus-leaf wrap and sprinkle with sesame seeds.",
    "Fold the lotus-leaf wrap into a triangle and serve hot."
